@base = https://api.harmoni.cc

### Root health check
GET {{base}}/

###

### Register new user
POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@dummy.com",
  "password": "HarmoniTest2026!"
}

###

### Login (dummy user)
# @name login
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maya@dummy.com",
  "password": "HarmoniTest2026!"
}

###

### Login — store token for other requests
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Get my profile (requires token from login above)
GET {{base}}/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
